column5: You guys have all missed it.  Look at the feral hog hiding up the hydro pole.  He is trying to trick the hog into thinking he is fishing, once he has the opportunity out comes the 30-06.
Judging by his coat colours he should be fishing for rainbows instead......and really......what's wrong with his reel???????????  . the floatation one is pretty good........
LOL.. "His rod is on backward..."  hahahaaha..
hehehehe. Twocoda....... Toooo Funny.
Ha ha funny.. I didnt even notice his reel untill I read this..His rod is on backwords..Funny stuff
wow...took the words right out of my mouth...
i am guessing that that it's a defective reverse able handle
I don't blame him. He's a lefty.
Too much Appleton's Rum, its happened to me on occasion, in the same spot actually, usually with the late Don (Blackie) Blackmore and his pimped out psyedelic converted milk truck.
you were not involved in any trips into the heart of  town were you ..... lol    loyns said blackie was still alive ??
That's what i was thinking at first too.  Must have a big live Perch on for bait.

Blackie has long passed away. Lyons probably told you about the noodle rod of Blackies he has now brought out of the closet and uses on occasion at the river. Nooch even puts a Hardy fly reel on it like in the good old days.  Rumour has it, that Kovack is still on the green side though.
maybe that is where i messed up ..
"Rods on backward" bwaahhhh, thanks for that. lol...  I don't recognize him, but chances are he has his own show.
I finally figured it out, I think. Judging by his posture he should have taken that dump before he hit the ice.
Strong like bull, smart like streetcar.
this guy is fishing trout at the ganaraska river
Ya
yep ... he has no gloves ..
Well, Some people do everything backwards at some point, )))) lol
I LIKE TO CATCH THE SALMONS!
How the heck does his reel work?  I want one..
What about his reel.. the problem is he has no gloves right lol
His pants ain't tucked in ...  just wait until the wife sees that.
the rod in the holder has a fish on?
His rod is on backward
He didn't drill a hole for the business end of the new style butt balanced by tip rod maybe?  Michael
5 to many beers.???
his socks dont match...and his feet are on the wrong boots....backasswards
doesnt have a float suit on and he keeps passing wind?
fishing in the hole he just peed in?
i figured it out!!!!!....the blue car only has three wheels....DOH....how could i have missed that ...
Isn't there a funniest ice fishing picture contest currently happening? I don't see anything topping this one.
The pail is upside down, hasn't snagged anything yet.
Can't anyone see the Yellow Danger sign?
he seems to be walking on water? two lines in the river? awkward reel setup?
Well, I dont see any holes drilled..
I predict a terrbile birdnest coming on.
I would say that her choice of wardrobe is not particularly flattering... HH
